title: La Grande Orange
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An all-in-one coffee and breakfast bar, cafe, pizzeria, and grocery store with multiple outlets. The pizzeria is full service sit-down dining, and many can be made vegan; open Mon-Thur 4-10pm, Fri-Sun 11am-10pm. The cafe is grab-n-go style and has labeled veg choices (green leaf for vegetarian, orange leaf for vegan) -- try the spicy chickpea lettuce wraps and the vegan English muffins. Also a location at 3400 E Sky Harbor Blvd, Terminal 4 - D gates (past security).
